Alex Fraser Research Forest bụ 98.02 km2 nke ala okpueze na mpaghara Cariboo nké British Columbia, Canada

Ọ bụ Faculty of Forestry na Mahadum British Columbia na-achịkwa ya, iji mepụta ohere màkà agụmakwụkwọ, nyocha na ngosipụta nke njikwa ọhịa na-adịgide adịgide na ịmepụta ụkpụrụ na-adịgidere adịgide n'ụzọ ego
A na-akpọ ọhịa ahụ Alex Fraser ónyé bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị; a na-akpọkwa Alex Fraser Bridge na Vancouver áhà ya.
